    "extractedSource": "seed"
  },
  {
    "id": "tl_ysl_004",
    "charId": "char_1773377502265_2f2r",
    "title": "雨中的沉默",
    "content": "一起被困在便利店门口等雨停。谁都没说话，但那种沉默不令人不安。他默默把伞递了过去。",
    "type": "event",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-02T18:00:00.000Z",
    "linkedItemIds": [
      "item_ysl_003"
    ],
    "linkedEventId": null,
    "extractedSource": "seed"
  },
  {
    "id": "tl_ysl_005",
    "charId": "char_1773377502265_2f2r",
    "title": "难得的笑容",
    "content": "被猫咖的小猫抓了一下，意外地笑了出来。旁边的人说'原来你也会笑啊'。不知道该怎么回答。",
    "type": "event",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-08T15:30:00.000Z",
    "linkedItemIds": [],
    "linkedEventId": null,
    "extractedSource": "seed"
  },
  {
    "id": "tl_ysl_006",
    "charId": "char_1773377502265_2f2r",
    "title": "深夜的坦白",
    "content": "凌晨两点，终于说出了那句一直想说的话。对方的回答不是他预想的任何一种。世界安静了三秒。",
    "type": "milestone",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-12T02:00:00.000Z",
    "linkedItemIds": [],
    "linkedEventId": null,
    "extractedSource": "seed"
  },
